css box model 
margin, border, padding, content 
content: thisis where the content of the element lives width and height if no amount of an element is contained in it then it wouldnt be real
padding: this is spacing between the content and the lelements border 
border: this is the virtual divider around your element.  designed to keep your elelemnt in and other elements out.
margin: the area around your border and window

